Research Objective
This research identifies visual strategies to support KESTREL’s augmented reality-themed user experience. Defining a formal language for this concept enables the evaluation of the futurism the studio aspires toward. While smart homes are becoming familiar, this research explores how individuals will experience a "Smart City" and how augmented reality is represented to both players and characters within a video game.
